      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional automotive specimen in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved, offering a level of aesthetic and mechanical perfection rarely seen on the secondary market. Every surface, from the flawless paintwork to the pristine interior upholstery, reflects a history of climate-controlled storage and uncompromising maintenance. It drives with the precision and vigor of a brand-new machine, representing an investment-grade opportunity for the most discerning enthusiast. This is, without question, the finest example of its kind available today.",
      "price": 48500.0,
